# Trivy ignore file for known false positives or accepted risks
# Format: CVE ID per line, with optional comment
#
# Add entries here when a vulnerability:
# - Is a false positive for our usage
# - Has no available fix yet and is accepted risk
# - Only affects dev dependencies not shipped to production
#
# Example:
# CVE-2023-XXXXX  # dev-only dependency, not in production bundle
